property:value;
}
ex: h1{ color:red; }
CSS styling 3 types:
Inline CSS
Internal CSS
External CSS --> 90%
Selectors types:
1.*
2.tag or element
3.[ .class]
4.[ #id ]

CSS:Day2
--------
Text Styling properties:
Gil roy font download

p{
font-family:cursive;
font-size:50px;
font-style:oblique; | italiac;
font-weight:900; =>Bold
line-height:0.8; 1; 1.5, 2;
letter-spacing: 5px;
word-spacing: 20px;
text-align: center; //left, right
text-transform: uppercase/lowercase/capitalize
text-decoration-line: underline/overline/line-through;
text-decoration-color: green;
text-decoration-style: dotted/double/wavy;
text-decoration:underline,none; //you can give above all three here
text-shadow: 3px 3px 3px violet;

}

hex code you can find colors there.
background-color:#fbbc05;
background-color:rgb(255,255,255)
background-color:rgba(50%,50%,3% ) -> you can give percentages

CSSDay3:**
---------
BoxModel:

div-> closed container
Box: height width padding margin model

//div box model syntax
.box{
height:200px;
width:200px;
background-color:brown;
padding:20px;
box-sizing: content-box;// 220px+20px height/width +padding
ex: Tents you can extend
box-sizing: border-box; // here No extension ex: Own house/Flat
}

//paragraph borders
p{
border-width:5px;
border-style: solid
border-color: red
border-radius:10px
}

//background image setting
.bg{
height:500px;
width:500px;
background-image: url('.........');
background-size: cover;
background-position: center;

//linear gradient colors
background-image:linear-graident(to right red,blue,green)

}

//radial gradient-> ellipse,circle
    height: 500px;
    width: 700px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellips at center ,red,orange,blue);
    box-shadow: 20px 20px 120px black;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at center ,red,orange,blue);
    box-shadow: 20px 20px 120px black;


CSSDay4:*
---------

download a font
add that to your folder
it is a .ttf file means true-type-font file
Register in CSS File:
@font-face{
font-family: MyPoppin;
src:url(./Poppins-Light.ttf)
}

h1{
  color: blueviolet;
    background-color: yellowgreen;
    font-family: MyPoppin;
}
//you can import a poppin in to css file
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playwrite+US+Trad+Guides&display=swap');
h1{
    color: blueviolet;
    background-color: yellowgreen;
    font-family: "Playwrite US Trad Guides", cursive;
}

